data.description: Welcome to 100 Burning Bush Place in La Plata, MD!  This charming one-story home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style with a range of exquisite features. As you step into this immaculate residence, you'll be immediately captivated by the warm and inviting atmosphere it provides.  Key Features:  One Level Living: Convenience is at the forefront of this home's design. Enjoy easy access to all areas of the house without the hassle of stairs.  Cherry Hardwood Floors: The rich, cherry hardwood floors add a touch of elegance to this home, creating a sense of warmth and luxury. These floors extend throughout the main living spaces, enhancing the visual appeal.  Kitchen with Granite Counters: The heart of the home, this kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops. The perfect space for preparing meals and entertaining guests, it's a chef's dream come true.  Screened In Porch and Grilling Porch: Embrace the joys of outdoor living with not one but two fabulous porches. The screened-in porch offers a peaceful retreat for relaxation, while the grilling porch is ideal for hosting outdoor gatherings with friends and family.  Open Floor Plan: The open floor plan promotes a sense of togetherness, making it easy to transition from the kitchen to the living and dining areas. This layout is perfect for both daily living and entertaining.  1865 Square Feet of Living Space: With 1865 square feet of living space, this home offers ample room for comfortable living. The layout is thoughtfully designed to maximize every square foot.  Immaculate Condition: This home has been meticulously cared for and maintained, ensuring that it's in pristine condition. You can move in with confidence, knowing that you're getting a home that's been lovingly looked after.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 100 Burning Bush Place your new home in La Plata, MD. With its one-level living, stunning cherry hardwood floors, granite-countered kitchen, screened and grilling porches, open floor plan, and immaculate condition, it's a rare find in today's market. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the comfort and charm this home has to offer.
